data.description: Are you looking for your dream home in the highly sought-after community of Ka Makana at Hoakalei? This recently remodeled gem boasts 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, offering the perfect blend of comfort and style. Tasteful enhancements, such as new luxury vinyl plank floors, several new appliances, and fresh interior and exterior paint, emphasize the modern luxury of the open space and the natural lighting from the Ewa sun. Home offers a bedroom and full bath on the first floor, great for extended family or office space. Lower your utility bill with leased PV system! Community offers resort like recreation areas featuring tennis/pickleball courts, parks/playgrounds and dog parks. Home is conveniently located near all military installations, Ewa Beach shopping centers, restaurants, Ka Makana Alii Mall, schools, UH West Oahu and the 2nd city of Kapolei! Don't miss the opportunity to make this refreshed and beautiful property your new home!
